      "content": "It makes perfect sense that you feel like a burden when you've spent a lifetime giving so much. Your desire to let go so they can be free speaks to how much you value their happiness. Instead of viewing yourself as a subtraction, see yourself as an opportunity for them to give back to you, which is a natural cycle of love. Please know that your presence matters, and there are ways to ease the strain without disappearing.",
