    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i hear what you're saying, but it doesn't feel like an opportunity to me. it feels like a drain. i look at them and i just see the hours they lose because of my failing body. if i wasnt here, they could finally just live their lives without constantly worrying about if i tripped or if i ate today. wouldnt it be more peaceful for everyone if the burden was just gone? wouldn't that be a more loving way to handle it?",
